are invited.

04:43.917 --> 04:45.578
- Saturday, huh?
- RALPH: Yeah.

04:45.719 --> 04:47.186
Well, I'll tell you something,
gentlemen.

04:47.320 --> 04:48.811
I'm very sorry I can't make it.

04:48.955 --> 04:50.548
Saturday, I'm taking Blossom
to dinner.

04:50.690 --> 04:53.888
I want to see just about
how much bunny she really is.

04:55.929 --> 04:57.954
