04:59.699 --> 05:01.463
Come on, Fonz.
Our party's going to be better.

05:01.601 --> 05:02.967
It's a college party.

05:03.103 --> 05:04.400
- A college party?
Are you kidding? -College?

05:04.538 --> 05:06.802
Oh, I just love
intellectual men.

05:06.940 --> 05:08.271
Oh, please, Fonz, let's go.

05:08.408 --> 05:10.376
Well, I'll tell you something.
I...

05:10.510 --> 05:12.001
We're going.

05:12.145 --> 05:13.272
All right, all right.

05:13.413 --> 05:15.143
