to do with it?

06:33.093 --> 06:34.151
Yes, dear, she's right.

06:34.294 --> 06:35.887
What has that got to do with it?

06:36.029 --> 06:37.087
- Marion.
- Well...

06:37.230 --> 06:39.028
Get over here.

06:39.165 --> 06:42.158
Didn't you have a talk with her
about that?

06:42.302 --> 06:43.770
Oh, that.

06:43.903 --> 06:45.895
Well, I told her everything.

06:46.039 --> 06:47.336
Everything?

06:47.474 --> 06:49.670
Well, everything
I could remember.

06:53.313 --> 06:54.542
That settles it.

06:54.681 --> 06:56.274
You are absolutely not going.

06:56.416 --> 06:58.282
I will not have
a daughter of mine

06:58.418 --> 07:00.853
-out car-dating
with some... gigolo! -Oh.

