07:03.123 --> 07:04.147
Uh, he's a senior.

07:04.291 --> 07:07.852
Yes. And Joanie says
he is a hunk.

07:07.994 --> 07:09.428
JOANIE:
Mm-hmm.

07:09.562 --> 07:10.996
A hunk?

07:11.131 --> 07:13.861
Oh, Howard, he sounds
like a very nice boy.

07:14.000 --> 07:15.058
HOWARD:
A hunk?

07:15.201 --> 07:16.828
And I wasn't any older
than Joanie

07:16.970 --> 07:19.405
