all right?

10:22.956 --> 10:24.719
Now, you drive, I'm Joanie.

10:24.858 --> 10:26.086
I'm your date, all right?

10:26.226 --> 10:27.284
- All right.
- Here we go. -Oh.

10:27.427 --> 10:28.621
Plant yourself, plant yourself.

10:28.761 --> 10:30.491
- I'm driving.
- You're driving. Here we are.

10:30.630 --> 10:32.621
(imitates engine revving)

10:34.334 --> 10:35.631
(imitates tires squealing)

10:35.768 --> 10:37.930
