10:38.071 --> 10:40.039
We're playing parked here.

10:40.173 --> 10:41.572
Oh, I'm sorry. I'm sorry.

10:41.708 --> 10:43.676
I just... I always get
a little carried away

10:43.810 --> 10:45.300
when I drive
these foreign couches.

10:45.445 --> 10:47.971
(Richie laughs)

10:48.114 --> 10:49.309
(Richie clears throat)

10:49.449 --> 10:51.110
All right, we're on the date,
I'm Joanie.

10:51.251 --> 10:53.310
Here we go. Let's try, uh...

10:53.453 --> 10:56.081
Let's try, "It's, uh...
it's getting very warm in here.

10:56.222 --> 10:58.748
- I got to roll down the window"
routine. -Uh-huh.

10:58.892 --> 11:00.484
I want you to watch every move.

11:00.627 --> 11:02.857
