to touch that girl.

11:32.959 --> 11:34.393
(laughs)

11:34.527 --> 11:36.052
You understand?

11:36.195 --> 11:38.027
That's called changing his tune.

11:38.164 --> 11:39.291
(Richie laughs)

11:39.432 --> 11:40.900
All right.

11:41.034 --> 11:42.297
All right, let's try, uh...

11:42.435 --> 11:44.631
Let's try the old,
um, stretch routine.

11:44.771 --> 11:46.329
- Oh, right. Right.
- Do you know it?

11:46.472 --> 11:49.237
- I always had good luck
with that one. -All right.

11:49.375 --> 11:51.503
Watch every move.

11:51.644 --> 11:53.510
(sighs)
Ah, memories.

11:53.646 --> 11:54.875
Used to call me
Stretch Cunningham.

11:55.014 --> 11:57.643
Yeah, right, just...
stretch, Cunningham.

11:57.784 --> 12:00.082
(yawning)

12:00.219 --> 12:02.518
(inhales deeply)

12:02.655 --> 12:04.715
- Mmm.
-(high-pitched): Ooh!

12:06.659 --> 12:08.650
(high-pitched giggling)

12:10.863 --> 12:12.126
(Richie grunts)

12:13.700 --> 12:15.691
(Richie groans)

12:18.004 --> 12:20.803
Oh, boy, that-that does
bring back memories.

12:20.940 --> 12:24.137
See, but that never stopped
old Stretch Cunningham.

12:24.277 --> 12:25.767
Oh, please, sweetheart.

12:25.912 --> 12:27.971
I was only trying
to give you a kiss.

12:28.114 --> 12:30.742
All right, now, this is
your part, Joanie, all right?

12:30.883 --> 12:32.875
(high-pitched):
Not on a first date!

12:34.287 --> 12:36.483
FONZIE: All right,
you got everything there?

12:36.623 --> 12:38.454
For every action a man's got,

12:38.591 --> 12:40.992
-you got a counteraction,
you dig it? -Why?

