BOTH:
What?

12:44.597 --> 12:47.089
Well, I mean,
I've never kissed before.

12:47.233 --> 12:48.325
I'm 15. I want a...

12:48.468 --> 12:49.799
I want a real kiss.

12:49.936 --> 12:52.769
I want to use... both lips.

12:57.210 --> 12:58.268
(car horn blares)

12:58.411 --> 12:59.537
Oh, there he is.

12:59.679 --> 13:02.910
Mom. Mom. Mom, do I look okay?
Do I look okay?

13:03.049 --> 13:05.245
- Hi. I'm David O'Dooley.
- Hello.

13:05.385 --> 13:09.481
Well, I'm Howard Cunningham,
Joanie's father.

13:09.622 --> 13:11.249
This is Joanie's mother.

13:11.391 --> 13:12.915
Incredible. You look so young.

13:13.059 --> 13:14.618
- Oh, thank you.
- Thank you.

13:14.761 --> 13:16.422
-(Joanie chuckles)
