13:33.946 --> 13:37.041
Well, good night, everyone.

13:37.183 --> 13:39.914
If you need me,

13:40.053 --> 13:42.647
you know where I'll be.

13:49.095 --> 13:50.085
Well, we better leave, Joanie.

13:50.229 --> 13:51.162
Oh, yeah.
(laughs quietly)

13:51.297 --> 13:52.992
Uh, we're going
to a Hawaiian party.

13:53.132 --> 13:55.123
- Oh.
- Oh.

13:56.436 --> 13:57.528
Hawaiian.

13:57.670 --> 13:59.695
Well, aloha.

13:59.839 --> 14:02.240
Say something
in Hawaiian, Howard.

14:02.375 --> 14:04.366
Be home early.

14:05.712 --> 14:07.111
Well, have a good time.

14:07.246 --> 14:09.010
- Yeah, bye. See you later.
- Thanks. Nice meeting you.

14:09.148 --> 14:11.674
- Bye. Good night.
- And drive carefully, now.

14:11.818 --> 14:13.149
- Yeah, we will.
- We will.

14:13.286 --> 14:14.549
Aw.

14:14.687 --> 14:17.156
Well, there she goes.

14:17.290 --> 14:20.259
Our little girl,
on her very first car date.

14:20.393 --> 14:22.623
- Isn't it nice, Howard?
-(sighs)

14:22.762 --> 14:26.391
I mean, think back to how it was
when you were young.

14:26.532 --> 14:28.523
