14:44.751 --> 14:46.878
Ralph, what's going on here?
It's freezing.

14:47.019 --> 14:49.181
A stroke of luck, Rich--
the boiler busted.

14:49.322 --> 14:51.313
There's no heat
for the rest of the night.

14:52.492 --> 14:54.483
Great party, huh?

14:57.430 --> 14:58.920
Why did you open the window?

14:59.065 --> 15:00.794
Rich, it's called ingenuity.

15:00.933 --> 15:03.232
It's too cold for
a "welcome to Hawaii" party,

15:03.369 --> 15:05.667
so I made it
a "welcome Alaska" party.

15:05.805 --> 15:08.797
I seized the moment. You get it?

15:08.941 --> 15:10.170
Yeah, I-l got it.

15:10.309 --> 15:11.538
Your brain is frozen.

15:11.677 --> 15:13.043
Right, right, right.

15:13.179 --> 15:15.910
Take off your coats, everyone.
Make yourself comfortable.

15:19.252 --> 15:22.153
Alaska, Alaska.

15:22.288 --> 15:23.687
Ralph.

15:23.823 --> 15:25.586
Ralph, you're out of control.

15:29.162 --> 15:31.187
Potsie, uh, are you
gonna let him get away

15:31.330 --> 15:32.855
With this Alaska bit?

15:32.999 --> 15:36.162
Want some ice cream?

15:36.302 --> 15:37.997
You guys make great roomies.

15:38.137 --> 15:41.505
You know, the nights
are six months long in Alaska.

15:41.641 --> 15:42.631
(both laugh)

15:42.775 --> 15:45.301
Good thing I slept late
this morning.

15:45.444 --> 15:47.572
Oh, come on, guys,
it's ridiculous.

15:47.713 --> 15:49.409
At least close the icebox.

15:49.549 --> 15:51.141
(laughs)

15:51.284 --> 15:53.946
I'm freezing.
Can I get inside your coat?

15:54.086 --> 15:56.317
Oh, well, I, uh...

15:56.455 --> 15:58.083
Oh.

15:58.224 --> 16:00.249
Alaska is... nice.

16:00.393 --> 16:01.917
(chuckles)

16:03.329 --> 16:06.196
Oh, now I know why
you go to college.

16:06.332 --> 16:08.061
Yeah, so you can freeze.

16:08.201 --> 16:09.964
- It is cold in here.
- Hey, there's Richie.

16:10.102 --> 16:11.400
(door slams)

16:11.537 --> 16:12.732
Huh?

16:14.006 --> 16:15.497
Oh.

16:15.641 --> 16:17.735
Oh, uh...

16:17.877 --> 16:19.208
Oh, <i>I</i> got it.

16:19.345 --> 16:20.904
- I got it. Oh, good.
- What?

16:21.047 --> 16:24.107
You see, we're, uh... we're
playing charades here, uh...

16:24.250 --> 16:25.547
"Embraceable You."

16:25.685 --> 16:26.879
Yeah, oh, that's a good one.

16:27.019 --> 16:27.986
What a great clue.

16:28.120 --> 16:30.521
Yeah. Yeah, see,
we're playing charades.

16:30.656 --> 16:32.317
- Oh.
- Hey, uh, Potsie.

16:32.458 --> 16:34.188
Potsie, come on,
there are little kids here.

16:34.327 --> 16:36.762
Mm.

16:36.896 --> 16:40.059
RICHIE:
Uh... Potsie. Lori Beth.

16:40.199 --> 16:42.361
Lori Beth, what are you doing?
Come on.

16:42.501 --> 16:45.061
I'm trying to keep warm.

16:45.204 --> 16:46.865
Well, what do you think
the light's for?

16:47.006 --> 16:50.465
- Oh, good idea.
- Uh... Uh, Potsie.

16:50.610 --> 16:52.339
Potsie, come on,
let's-let's play. Let's...

16:52.478 --> 16:54.708
Let's do the next charade,
okay? Come on, anything.

16:57.483 --> 17:00.111
All right: lights, lips, action.

17:00.253 --> 17:01.311
Oh.

17:01.454 --> 17:03.820
- Joanie's here.
- Joanie's here.

17:10.896 --> 17:12.922
Fonz, uh, this
is David O'Dooley.

17:13.065 --> 17:15.159
- Hi.
- Hey, hello, car date.

17:17.036 --> 17:19.198
This here is, uh, Blossom.

17:19.338 --> 17:20.771
She just got off work.

17:20.906 --> 17:21.839
She's a bunny.

17:21.973 --> 17:23.738
Outstanding.

17:23.876 --> 17:25.401
RICHIE:
What are we gonna do now, gang?

17:25.544 --> 17:26.671
FONZIE:
All right, let's dance.

17:37.590 --> 17:39.149
You want to dance?

17:39.292 --> 17:41.283
In this cold,
we better keep moving.

17:51.504 --> 17:52.528
(indistinct whisper)

17:52.672 --> 17:53.730
What?

17:53.873 --> 17:55.204
We have to.

17:55.341 --> 17:57.503
We have to set a good example
for the kids. Please. Please.

17:57.643 --> 17:58.770
We're just dancing.

17:58.911 --> 18:00.606
For me.

18:00.746 --> 18:02.646
-(sighs) -Ah. Oh,
that's good, that's good.

18:02.782 --> 18:04.045
(chuckles)

18:04.183 --> 18:05.947
Hmm? Huh?

18:06.085 --> 18:07.678
Huh.

18:07.820 --> 18:09.811
(clears throat)

18:10.623 --> 18:11.715
(whispers):
Fonz.

18:11.857 --> 18:13.018
Not now, Rich.

18:13.159 --> 18:16.060
Got to set an example
for the kid.

18:16.195 --> 18:17.856
Kid.

18:17.997 --> 18:19.396
- Kid.
- Yeah, thanks.

18:19.532 --> 18:20.590
(Snaps fingers)

18:20.733 --> 18:22.724
Kid.

18:41.754 --> 18:43.347
