18:43.489 --> 18:46.720
We can't kiss, dance, nose,
snuggle, nothing.

18:47.960 --> 18:49.690
It's just like a regular date.

18:49.829 --> 18:51.820
RICHIE:
All right.

18:51.964 --> 18:53.989
All right, I'll, uh...
I'll talk to her.

18:54.133 --> 18:55.828
POTSIE and RALPH:
Well, talk.

18:55.968 --> 18:57.959
All right, I'm going to.

19:00.873 --> 19:02.398
(clears throat)
Uh, excuse me.

19:02.541 --> 19:04.510
Uh, I need to talk
to Joanie for a second.

19:04.643 --> 19:05.804
- Do you mind?
- Oh, no, sure.

19:05.945 --> 19:07.936
I'll be over at the lightbulb.

19:09.448 --> 19:11.178
What is it now?
Was I dancing too close?

19:11.317 --> 19:12.341
No, no.

19:12.485 --> 19:14.009
Joanie, see,
I'm your brother, and I...

19:14.153 --> 19:16.588
and I have to talk to you.
See, uh...

19:19.191 --> 19:20.784
See, I'm in college now.

19:20.926 --> 19:22.622
Good, Rich,
but I already know that.

19:22.762 --> 19:26.129
What I'm trying to say
is this is a college party.

19:26.265 --> 19:29.064
Now, you two are still
little kids. There's...

19:29.201 --> 19:31.227
Rich, I get it.

19:31.370 --> 19:32.428
You don't want me around.

19:32.571 --> 19:34.130
Hey, that's fine
with me, big brother.

19:34.273 --> 19:37.243
Come on, David, we're leaving.

19:39.311 --> 19:41.746
Oh, yeah, no, uh, I was just
taking my bunny for a walk.

19:41.881 --> 19:44.042
You know, uh...
♪ Da, da, da, de, da, da. ♪

19:44.183 --> 19:46.083
All right, all right,
all right. Look, uh...

19:46.218 --> 19:47.550
Hey, let me ask you a question.

19:47.686 --> 19:49.154
Why you going?

19:49.288 --> 19:52.315
I'm leaving
because of my big brother.

19:54.126 --> 19:56.993
He doesn't want me around
because he thinks I'm a kid.

19:57.129 --> 19:58.893
Well, this is for you.

19:59.031 --> 20:01.022
(blows raspberry)

20:02.168 --> 20:03.499
Did you see what she just did?

20:03.636 --> 20:05.570
Did you see what she
did to me? She went...

20:05.704 --> 20:07.673
(blows raspberry)

20:07.807 --> 20:09.832
Can you believe she did that?
(blows raspberry)

20:09.975 --> 20:11.102
Just like a little kid.

20:11.243 --> 20:12.506
(blows raspberry)

20:12.645 --> 20:13.874
What do you think of that?

20:14.013 --> 20:15.481
(all blow raspberries)

20:20.252 --> 20:22.187
-(car door closes)
- They're here, Marion.

20:22.321 --> 20:24.187
Oh, I knew he'd
bring her back on time.

20:24.323 --> 20:25.484
I wasn't worried.

20:25.624 --> 20:26.785
No?

20:26.926 --> 20:30.453
- Then why are you watering
artificial plants? -Oh.

20:31.497 --> 20:32.828
- Hi.
- Hi.

20:32.965 --> 20:33.932
- Oh, you're back.
- Yeah.

20:34.066 --> 20:35.397
Oh, did you have a nice time?

20:35.534 --> 20:37.093
- Mmm, outstanding.
- Yeah.

20:37.236 --> 20:39.136
How outstanding?

20:39.271 --> 20:40.603
Howard.

20:40.740 --> 20:43.971
Oh. Well, uh, I'm glad
everything worked out.

20:44.110 --> 20:46.579
Well, it's time to say
good night, Joanie.

20:46.712 --> 20:47.736
It's after 11:00.

20:47.880 --> 20:49.644
(short laugh)

20:49.782 --> 20:51.079
I'll be up in a minute, Dad.

20:51.217 --> 20:52.946
Well, why don't you
come on up with us?

20:53.085 --> 20:54.075
Howard.

20:54.220 --> 20:56.051
What? Oh.

20:56.188 --> 20:57.315
Well, okay.

20:57.456 --> 20:58.480
- Good night.
- Good night.

20:58.624 --> 21:00.388
- Good night. -Good night.
- Good night.

21:00.526 --> 21:01.516
- Good night, dear.
- Yeah, good night.

21:01.660 --> 21:02.787
- It was nice meeting you.
- Good night.

21:02.928 --> 21:04.294
- Oh, nice to have met you, too.
- Thank you. -Good night.

21:04.430 --> 21:06.159
- Good night. -Good night.

21:06.298 --> 21:08.062
- Good night.
- Good night.

21:08.200 --> 21:09.099
(laughs)

21:09.235 --> 21:10.600
Parents.

21:10.736 --> 21:11.999
Oh, yeah.

