You sure are pretty.

21:15.641 --> 21:17.336
I am?

21:18.377 --> 21:19.674
HOWARD:
Joanie!

21:19.812 --> 21:22.508
I'll be right up, Dad.

21:22.648 --> 21:24.810
I think my dad was afraid
that you're, uh,

21:24.950 --> 21:27.317
gonna try and kiss me.

21:27.453 --> 21:29.148
He is?

21:29.288 --> 21:31.188
Uh-huh.

21:31.323 --> 21:33.883
- HOWARD: Joanie!
- Ah! On my way, Dad.

21:34.026 --> 21:36.017
(quick laugh)

21:47.206 --> 21:50.301
I guess your dad was right.

21:50.442 --> 21:53.901
Well, uh, guess I better
take you home now.

21:59.318 --> 22:00.979
L-I think I am home.

22:02.388 --> 22:03.821
(both laugh)

22:03.956 --> 22:04.923
- Yeah.
- I am.

22:05.057 --> 22:06.081
Well, uh...

22:06.225 --> 22:07.385
I guess I better go, then.

22:07.526 --> 22:09.358
Oh, oh, uh, uh, yeah,

22:09.495 --> 22:11.361
(laughing):
I'll open the door.

22:11.497 --> 22:13.488
Yeah. Say, uh...

22:15.568 --> 22:17.297
- HOWARD: Marion!
- Oh.

22:17.436 --> 22:19.461
MARION:
Joanie!

22:19.605 --> 22:20.697
Uh...

22:20.840 --> 22:21.966
Thanks for the evening,
and, uh...

22:22.107 --> 22:23.097
