23:47.059 --> 23:48.925
Oh. Oh, yeah.

23:49.061 --> 23:51.086
Rich, uh...

23:51.230 --> 23:52.925
do you think I'm pretty?

23:53.065 --> 23:55.534
Well, I think so, but,
you know, I'm your brother.

23:55.668 --> 23:57.727
I'm not sure that counts.

23:57.870 --> 24:00.930
I do know that a lot of guys
think you're very pretty.

24:01.073 --> 24:03.508
- Yeah?
- Yeah.

24:03.642 --> 24:05.576
- Oh, thanks.
- That's okay.

24:06.712 --> 24:09.340
Joanie...
(clears throat)

24:09.481 --> 24:11.507
Do, uh, girls at Arnold's

24:11.650 --> 24:14.449
think that I'm, uh...

24:14.586 --> 24:16.452
you know...

24:16.588 --> 24:18.147
handsome?

24:18.290 --> 24:19.849
Well, yeah, some of them
think you're handsome.

24:19.992 --> 24:21.118
(Richie chuckles)

24:21.260 --> 24:23.160
But I can't imagine why
with all those freckles.

24:23.295 --> 24:24.729
-(laughs)
.l-ley.

24:24.863 --> 24:26.456
